{# Citation policy that scanners can opt into. Call as `{{ cite_in('reasoning') }}` or `{{ cite_in('summary') }}`. #}
{%- macro cite_in(field_name) -%}
Inside `{{ field_name }}`, cite key moments as `(t <seconds>)` using the footer's `REC_T` value, e.g. `(t 92)`. One moment per parens; max 1–2 citations per paragraph. Cite only turning points, blockers, and climaxes — skip routine navigation. Use whole seconds read from the footer; never cite a time you haven't seen on the footer.
{%- endmacro -%}
